metadata.name: MAHSA AMINi
metadata.description: We should not let Mahsa's blood be trampled We must help his family and the people of Iran And prepare food for them so that they can stand in front of the Iranian government Please purchase this artwork so we can help. On 16 September 2022, a 22-year-old Iranian woman named Mahsa Amini, also known as Zhina Amini or Jîna Emînî, died in Tehran, Iran, under suspicious circumstances while in police custody, potentially due to police
